Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...head for the New World,\Nthe second half of the Grand Line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:53.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:03:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.29,0:03:06.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned to rubber \Nafter he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.69,0:03:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.97,0:03:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.51,0:03:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.91,0:03:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a \Npirate alliance with Trafalgar Law{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and have come to Dressrosa\Nto hand Caesar over to Doflamingo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Luffy found out that the \Nprize for a fighting event
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:34.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,was the Flare-Flare Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he decided to enter and fight fierce \Nbattles against other tough
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:39.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,contenders from the New World.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come after me, Doflamingo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.13,0:03:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is he gonna go across the bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.31,0:04:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Doflamingo!\NThey have nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.03,0:04:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over, Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Doflamingo is flying towards us!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?! A nightmare?!\NAre we gonna get killed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.77,0:04:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch this, Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll viciously slay your allies\Nright before your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tra-guy, help...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friends are crying in fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.29,0:04:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave them alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes quite a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"A Big Clash!\NSanji vs. Doflamingo!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the "Black Foot" of \Nthe Straw Hats, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diable Jambe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Premiere Hachis Hash!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pentachromatic Strings!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sanji-{\i1}san{\i0}!\N--What did Doflamingo do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save your friends if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Doflamingo is coming this way!\N--You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:05:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stay away from us!\N--Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diable Jambe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Poele a Frire...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Spectre!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's powerful! He's quite strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:07:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What happened? I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Sanji-{\i1}san{\i0} got frozen in mid air!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been grappled\Nby the Young Master's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo's power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Foot is like a bug caught\Nin a spider's web now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All he can do is wait for death!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What is it?!\N--A whip?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything! Just run!\NUse Coup de Burst to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Overheat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away, Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shambles!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:08:01.20,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,DRESSROSA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tra-guy! He saved Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.99,0:08:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I made a mistake!\NLet's get on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tra-guy-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I'm on the ship again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.37,0:08:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Giolla! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being held captive, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dropped my guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Doflamingo's coming again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.80,0:09:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Foot-{\i1}ya{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the plan to destroy\Nthe factory going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found out where it is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Franky said it's gonna \Nbe harder than we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's my father?! And Kanjuro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.19,0:09:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NSan-goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are they doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momonosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The samurai is heading to the factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.06,0:09:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be alright once everything is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we need more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!\NIs that my heart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you keeping it in the cabin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had your heart with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You had it in your body the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to take him\Nand head for Zou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.21,0:10:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zou?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave you the Vivre Card\Nthat leads you to the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a Vivre Card?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It'll point toward an island called Zou\Nthat I talked about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head for the island?!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.74,0:10:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0} and the others?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing left to do on this island is\Ndestroy the factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll catch up with you guys soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.84,0:10:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! We'll wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't set sail without our captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.78,0:10:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:11:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy ship is flying towards us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is that possible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.48,0:11:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It must be Fujitora.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo is coming from that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy ship is getting closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.29,0:11:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can wait here if you want\Nbut don't let them take Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's falling from the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meteorites?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.99,0:12:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tra-guy-{\i1}kun{\i0}, we "Spiral Hats" are\Ngonna leave now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.07,0:12:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realize we have\Nto carry Caesar as far as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's clear we have to leave here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought Dressrosa was just a waypoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our main purpose was killing Kaido \Nof the Four Emperors, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you getting too hung up\Non Doflamingo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meteorites! Meteorites!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:13:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Issho-{\i1}san{\i0}, they hit the bottom of our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.41,0:13:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, I hadn't thought about that.\NLaw-{\i1}san{\i0} is there, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you stop eating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.90,0:13:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get back to Dressrosa now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the war...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will turn, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell them to turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, ready?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whip, again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joker! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excess Whip String!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-{\i1}ya{\i0}! Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.16,0:14:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to sail where there are no clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo is a String-String Fruit eater!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He moves through the air\Nby attaching strings to clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't follow you if there are no clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strings? I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.66,0:15:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready for Coup de Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law, what do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master-{\i1}sama{\i0}, don't worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you!\NI want to ask you something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you on the second floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking to you! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can't you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.61,0:15:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just met my hero - Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0} today
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now, Zoro-{\i1}senpai{\i0} is talking to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop crying from happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI wonder who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.64,0:16:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I don't know who you are
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nbut can you tell us how to enter the Colosseum?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.39,0:16:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the doors are closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z-Zoro-{\i1}senpai{\i0} is asking me a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad that I sailed out to the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like he got very excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.76,0:16:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, calm down and listen. We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.37,0:16:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you were there to see it, Zoro-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.52,0:16:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0} was awesome as hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:17:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard him say Luffy-{\i1}dono{\i0}\Nand Zoro-{\i1}dono{\i0}'s names now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he know who you two are?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the battle royal here\Nin the Corrida Colosseum!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only one winner from Block D can\Nmove to the finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are all fighting intensely\Nto get that one spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The way she moves...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.99,0:17:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI don't think she's just another gladiator.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.79,0:17:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why doesn't she make an \Nattack even passing up
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:18:05.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,some critical chances?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is she doing?!\NShe's at the edge of the ring!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better worry about yourself\Nbefore you worry about someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.57,0:18:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop backing up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're at the edge now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Stay at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.65,0:18:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.43,0:19:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare for death, you little tramp!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just finish her off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.56,0:19:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.18,0:19:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my girl, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.39,0:19:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did she just do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we barely outran\Nthe Navy and Doflamingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna head for Zou.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? No, wait, Sanji!\NAre you gonna leave us?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get through somehow and meet us there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready to get away\Nas soon as I have a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.19,0:20:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, we'll be alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go to Zou (elephant)\Nor Giraffe or wherever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.87,0:20:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna destroy the factory for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.87,0:20:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are Luffy and Law doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro and Kin'emon went\Nto tell Luffy what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.98,0:20:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.23,0:21:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point in letting half \Nof the Straw Hats get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.17,0:21:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other half is in Dressrosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:21:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I take them as hostages,\Nthey'll come back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:22:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,right away to return Caesar to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.78,0:22:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that you knew\Nthere are quite a few people...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.78,0:22:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who underestimated them like that\Nand got burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.13,0:22:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid that I have to break up my alliance\Nwith the Straw Hats now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.97,0:22:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I joined forces with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.04,0:22:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my only purpose was to use them\Nto stop the manufacture of SMILEs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.68,0:22:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I can't kill you right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaido will kill you sooner or later\Nonce you lose all the SMILEs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.49,0:22:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.06,0:22:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're gonna sacrifice \Nyourself to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.46,0:22:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see how the world \Nfalls into a mess after you die,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.07,0:23:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but more importantly, I want to make \Nyou pay for what you did 13 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.61,0:23:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joker!
